        "Result1": "\\begin{aligned}\n\n&\\text{We get 4 terms.}\n\\end{aligned}",
        "Explanation1": "\\begin{aligned}\n(x+\\sqrt{x^{2}-1})^{6} & = {}^6C_{0}\\cdot\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{6} + {}^6C_{1}\\cdot x\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{5} +{}^6C_{2}\\cdot x^2\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{4}+{}^6C_{3}\\cdot x^3\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{3}+...\\\\\n(x-\\sqrt{x^{2}-1})^{6} & = {}^6C_{0}\\cdot\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{6} - {}^6C_{1}\\cdot x\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{5} +{}^6C_{2}\\cdot x^2\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{4}-{}^6C_{3}\\cdot x^3\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{3}+...\\\\\n\\therefore (x+\\sqrt{x^{2}-1})^{6}+ (x-\\sqrt{x^{2}-1})^{6} &= 2\\cdot ({}^6C_{0}\\cdot\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{6} + {}^6C_{2}\\cdot x^2\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{4} +{}^6C_{4}\\cdot x^4\\left(\\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\\right)^{2}+{}^6C_{6}\\cdot x^6)\\\\\n&=2\\cdot ({}^6C_{0}\\cdot\\left(x^{2}-1\\right)^{3} + {}^6C_{2}\\cdot x^2\\left(x^{2}-1\\right)^{2} +{}^6C_{4}\\cdot x^4\\left(x^{2}-1\\right)+{}^6C_{6}\\cdot x^6)\\\\\n&= 2\\cdot((x^6 - 1 - 3x^2\\cdot(x^2-1)) ~+~ {}^6C_{2}\\cdot x^2\\cdot(x^4 +1 -2x^2) ~+~ {}^6C_{4}\\cdot (x^6-x^4)~+~ {}^6C_{6}\\cdot x^6 )\\\\\n&\\text{Simplifying this we get}\\\\\n&=2\\cdot(x^6\\cdot(1+{}^6C_{2}+{}^6C_{4}+{}^nC_{6}) - x^4\\cdot(3+2\\cdot{}^nC_{2} + {}^6C_{4}) + x^2\\cdot(3+{}^6C_{2}) +1)\n\\\\&\\therefore\\text{ We get 4 terms.}\n\\end{aligned}",
